  </p>
  <div class="p04__copy">
    <h2 class="p04__headline  twtr-type  twtr-color--white-neutral">
      Изменения в положениях настоящей Политики конфиденциальности
    </h2>
</div>
</div>
</div>


    
    
    <div class="cr01-section">


















<div class="cr01  twtr-gutter  cr01--section      twtr-color-bg--white-neutral      ">
  <div class="cr01__item  twtr-grid    " style="--theme-color: var(--blue-dark)">
    
      <div class="twtr-grid__col  twtr-grid__col-md-12">
        <div class="cr01__wrapper  ">
          




    
    
    <div class="cr01-section">


















<div class="cr01    cr01--block      twtr-color-bg--white-neutral      ">
  <div class="cr01__item  twtr-grid    " style="--theme-color: var(--blue-dark)">
    
